#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:383
msgid "Configure the endpoint to authenticate the user with its username/userid and password."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຜູ້ໃຊ້ດ້ວຍຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້/userid ແລະ ລະຫັດຜ່ານ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:403
msgid ""
"Configure the endpoint to create a new user in the user store. The above defined attributes can be\n"
"                set in the UI and will be added to the request body. Additionally, you can define a password which must\n"
"                be specified in the request mapping using the tag <code>\"{password}\"</code>."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອສ້າງຜູ້ໃຊ້ໃໝ່ໃນ user store. ຄຸນລັກສະນະທີ່ກຳນົດຂ້າງເທິງສາມາດ\n"
"                ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ UI ແລະ ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ request body. ນອກຈາກນີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົ"
"ດລະຫັດຜ່ານເຊິ່ງຕ້ອງ\n"
"                ຖືກລະບຸໃນ request mapping ໂດຍໃຊ້ແທັກ <code>\"{password}\"</code>."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:415
msgid "Configure the endpoint to delete an existing user from the user store."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອລຶບຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ມີຢູ່ອອກຈາກ user store."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:409
msgid ""
"Configure the endpoint to edit an existing user in the user store. The above defined attributes can\n"
"                be set in the UI and will be added to the request body. Additionally, you can define custom request\n"
"                parameters in the request mapping."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວໃນ user store. ຄຸນລັກສະນະທີ່ກຳນົດຂ້າງເທິງ\n"
"                ສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນ UI ແລະ ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ request body. ນອກຈາກນີ້, ທ່ານສາມ"
"າດກຳນົດ request\n"
"                parameters ແບບກຳນົດເອງໃນ request mapping."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:387
msgid ""
"Configure the endpoint to retrieve a list of users from the user store. The above defined attributes\n"
"                are added to the request as search parameters if they are available in the request."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອດຶງລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈາກ user store. ຄຸນລັກສະນະທີ່ກຳນົດຂ້າງເທິງ\n"
"                ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ request ເປັນພາລາມິເຕີຄົ້ນຫາ ຖ້າມີໃນ request."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:392
msgid ""
"Configure the endpoint to retrieve a single user for the UID. For example, privacyIDEA only stores\n"
"                the UID of the token owner. To resolve the complete user, this endpoint is used."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄົນດຽວສຳລັບ UID. ຕົວຢ່າງ, privacyIDEA ຈະເກັບ\n"
"                ພຽງ UID ຂອງເຈົ້າຂອງໂທເຄັນ. ເພື່ອ resolve ຜູ້ໃຊ້ໃຫ້ຄົບຖ້ວນ, endpoint ນີ້ຈະຖື"
"ກນຳໃຊ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:397
msgid ""
"Configure the endpoint to retrieve a single user for the username. For example, when a user tries to\n"
"                authenticate against privacyIDEA, only the username is provided. To resolve the complete user and\n"
"                evaluate if the user exists, this endpoint is used."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ endpoint ເພື່ອດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄົນດຽວສຳລັບຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ເມື່ອຜູ້ໃຊ້ພະຍາຍາມ\n"
"                ຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນກັບ privacyIDEA, ຈະມີພຽງຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຖືກສົ່ງມາ. ເພື່ອ resolve ຜູ້ໃຊ້ໃຫ້ຄົບ"
"ຖ້ວນ ແລະ\n"
"                ປະເມີນວ່າຜູ້ໃຊ້ມີຢູ່ຈິງຫຼືບໍ່, endpoint ນີ້ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້."

