msgid ""
"The Certificate Token lets you enroll an x509 ceritificate\n"
"    by the given CA."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.daypassword.html:2
msgid ""
"The DayPassword Token is a time based password token.\n"
"    It is based on the TOTP token, but it can be used more than once.."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.daypassword.html:1
msgid ""
"The DayPassword token is a time based password token. You can paste a secret key or\n"
"    have the server generate the secret and scan the QR code with an authenticator app that supports the token."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.email.html:2
msgid ""
"The EMail token is a challenge response token that sends the OTP value to\n"
"    the given email address, when the correct OTP PIN was presented by the user."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.email.html:1
msgid "The Email Token sends the OTP value to the users email address."
msgstr "ໂທເຄັນອີເມວສົ່ງຄ່າ OTP ໄປຍັງທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enrolled.tiqr.html:11
msgid "The Enrollment URL"
msgstr "URL ການລົງທະບຽນ"

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.hotp.html:2
msgid ""
"The HOTP Token is an event based one time password token.\n"
"    It is described in <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4226\">RFC\n"
"    4226</a>."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.hotp.html:1
msgid ""
"The HOTP token is an event based token. You can paste a secret key or\n"
"    have the server generate the secret and scan the QR code with a\n"
"    smartphone app like the privacyIDEA Authenticator turning your\n"
"    smartphone into an authentication device. You can also use other\n"
"    authenticator apps like Google Authenticator. But note, that these\n"
"    might have limitations in the supported hash algorithms or other parameters."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/login/views/login.html:102
msgid ""
"The HSM is not ready. privacyIDEA can not work properly. Please start\n"
"        the HSM and reload this page."
msgstr ""

