msgstr "ປະເພດ Credential ນີ້ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບການກວດສອບລະຫັດຜ່ານຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.system.doc.html:2
msgid ""
"This documentation contains the current\n"
"    configuration of your system in restructured text. You can use\n"
"    this to document your installed system."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.webauthn.html:19
msgid ""
"This does not need to be set for WebAuthn to work, however without\n"
"        this, privacyIDEA can not check, whether an attestation certificate is\n"
"        actually trusted (it will still be checked for validity). Therefore it\n"
"        is mandatory to set this, if webauthn_authenticator_attestation_level\n"
"        is set to \"trusted\" by a policy for any user."
msgstr ""

#: privacyidea/static/components/dialogs/views/dialog.about.html:17
msgid ""
"This is a Single Page Application client that acts as a\n"
"                        frontend for\n"
"                        privacyIDEA authentication backend."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນໜ້າດຽວທີ່ເຮັດໜ້າທີ່ເປັນ\n"
"                        ສ່ວນຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສຳລັບ\n"
"                        ລະບົບຫຼັງບ້ານການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງ privacyIDEA."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.yubikey.html:2
msgid ""
"This is a Yubikey in the Yubico Mode authenticated against privacyIDEA.\n"
"    The Yubikey emits a 44 character on time password."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນ Yubikey ໃນໂໝດ Yubico ທີ່ຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຜ່ານ privacyIDEA.\n"
"    Yubikey ຈະປ່ອຍລະຫັດຜ່ານໃຊ້ຄັ້ງດຽວທີ່ມີຄວາມຍາວ 44 ຕົວອັກສອນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.import.html:58
msgid ""
"This is an RFC6030 OATH compliant PSKC file.\n"
"            Values in the PSKC files may be unencrypted or\n"
"            <em>either</em> encrypted with a\n"
"            <em>Pre Shared Key</em> or <em>password</em>. If the values are\n"
"            encrypted, please specify the Pre Shared Key in hex format or the\n"
"            password."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ PSKC ທີ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັບ RFC6030 OATH.\n"
"            ຄ່າໃນໄຟລ໌ PSKC ອາດຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ເຂົ້າລະຫັດ ຫຼື\n"
"            <em>ອາດຈະ</em> ຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດດ້ວຍ\n"
"            <em>ກຸນແຈທີ່ແບ່ງປັນກັນໄວ້ (Pre Shared Key)</em> ຫຼື <em>ລະຫັດຜ່ານ</em>. ຖ້າຄ່າ"
"ເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ\n"
"            ຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດ, ກະລຸນາລະບຸ Pre Shared Key ໃນຮູບແບບເລກຖານສິບຫົກ ຫຼື\n"
"            ລະຫັດຜ່ານ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.caconnectors.local.html:132
msgid ""
"This is the CRL file, which is written when a certificate\n"
"                    is revoked or the CRL is created otherwise."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ CRL, ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກຂຽນຂຶ້ນເມື່ອໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ\n"
"                    ຖືກຍົກເລີກ ຫຼື ເມື່ອ CRL ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນກໍລະນີອື່ນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:79
msgid ""
"This is the OCRA suite used by the TiQR App.\n"
"        The default OCRA suite is OCRA-1:HOTP-SHA1-6:QN10.\n"
"        For more details see the\n"
"        <a href=\"http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6287#page-8\" target=\"OCRA\">RFC\n"
"            6287</a>."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊຸດ OCRA ທີ່ໃຊ້ໂດຍແອັບ TiQR.\n"
"        ຊຸດ OCRA ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ OCRA-1:HOTP-SHA1-6:QN10.\n"
"        ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມ ເບິ່ງໄດ້ທີ່\n"
"        <a href=\"http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6287#page-8\" "
"target=\"OCRA\">RFC\n"
"            6287</a>."

#: privacyidea/static/components/directives/views/directive.registerContainer.html:74
msgid ""
"This is the correct answer to the passphrase prompt the user has to enter to\n"
"                            successfully register the container."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຄຳຕອບທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງສຳລັບຄຳຖາມລະຫັດຜ່ານທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງປ້ອນເຂົ້າ\n"
"                            ເພື່ອລົງທະບຽນບັນຈຸ (container) ໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.caconnectors.local.html:115
msgid "This is the directory were certificates get written to."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນໄດເລກະທໍຣີທີ່ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນຈະຖືກຂຽນລົງໄປ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:33
msgid "This is the display name of your service in the TiQR app."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ສະແດງຜົນຂອງການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານໃນແອັບ TiQR."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.smtp.edit.html:63
msgid ""
"This is the email address of the\n"
"                sender. Usually this should be an email address identifying\n"
"                your system."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວຂອງ\n"
"                ຜູ້ສົ່ງ. ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວ ນີ້ຄວນເປັນທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວທີ່ລະບຸ\n"
"                ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.question.html:12
msgid "This is the number of answers a user needs to define to enroll a token."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນຈຳນວນຄຳຕອບທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງກຳນົດເພື່ອລົງທະບຽນໂທເຄັນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:43
msgid ""
"This is the service identifier that will be passed to the TiQR app.\n"
"        This should contain a reverse FQDN (defaults to org.privacyidea)."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຕົວລະບຸການບໍລິການທີ່ຈະສົ່ງໄປຍັງແອັບ TiQR.\n"
"        ມັນຄວນຈະບັນຈຸ FQDN ແບບປີ້ນກັບ (ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ org.privacyidea)."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.tokengroup.edit.html:22
msgid ""
"This is the unique identifying name\n"
"                for this group definition."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ລະບຸທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"                ສຳລັບຄຳນິຍາມກຸ່ມນີ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.serviceid.edit.html:22
msgid ""
"This is the unique identifying name\n"
"                for this service definition."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ລະບຸທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"                ສຳລັບຄຳນິຍາມການບໍລິການນີ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.radius.edit.html:22
msgid ""
"This is the unique identifying name\n"
"                of the RADIUS server definition."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ລະບຸທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"                ຂອງຄຳນິຍາມເຊີບເວີ RADIUS."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.smtp.edit.html:21
msgid ""
"This is the unique identifying name\n"
"                of the SMTP server definition."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ລະບຸທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"                ຂອງຄຳນິຍາມເຊີບເວີ SMTP."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.privacyideaserver.edit.html:22
msgid ""
"This is the unique identifying name\n"
"                of the privacyIDEA server definition."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ລະບຸທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"                ຂອງຄຳນິຍາມເຊີບເວີ privacyIDEA."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.radius.html:45
msgid ""
"This is the username that is sent\n"
"        to the RADIUS server. It can be different from the owner of this\n"
"        RADIUS token."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຊື່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງ\n"
"        ໄປຍັງເຊີບເວີ RADIUS. ມັນອາດຈະແຕກຕ່າງຈາກເຈົ້າຂອງ\n"
"        ໂທເຄັນ RADIUS ນີ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.registration.html:6
msgid ""
"This is used, so that the user can enroll a token on his own, after\n"
"    logging in for the first time."
msgstr ""
"ອັນນີ້ຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດລົງທະບຽນໂທເຄັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ, ຫຼັງຈາກ\n"
"    ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບຄັ້ງທຳອິດ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.u2f.html:13
msgid ""
"This must be a valid FQDN with also a valid top level domain -\n"
"        otherwise you might receive a U2F Error 2 (Bad Request)."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ຕ້ອງເປັນ FQDN ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ພ້ອມກັບໂດເມນລະດັບສູງສຸດ (top level domain) ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ -\n"
"        ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ທ່ານອາດຈະໄດ້ຮັບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ U2F Error 2 (Bad Request)."

#: privacyidea/static/components/directives/views/directive.registerContainer.html:51
msgid "This prompt will be displayed to the user."
msgstr "ຄຳຖາມນີ້ຈະຖືກສະແດງໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ເຫັນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:237
msgid ""
"This section allows to configure an endpoint to which the privacyIDEA server must authenticate in order\n"
"                to receive an access token. This token can then be used to access the user store API."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນນີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າປາຍທາງ (endpoint) ທີ່ເຊີບເວີ privacyIDEA ຕ້ອງຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ\n"
"                ເພື່ອຮັບ Access Token. ໂທເຄັນນີ້ສາມາດຖືກນຳໄປໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງ API ຂອງບ່ອນເກັ"
"ບຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ (user store)."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.ldap.html:241
msgid "This setting activates a LDAP server pool that is persisted between requests."
msgstr ""
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ກຸ່ມເຊີບເວີ LDAP (pool) ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກເກັບຮັກສາໄວ້ລະຫວ່າງການຮ້ອງຂໍ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.webauthn.html:13
msgid ""
"This should be a path to a local directory on the server, that\n"
"        privacyIDEA has read access to. It should contain certificate files.\n"
"        Any certificates in this directory will be trusted to correctly attest\n"
"        authenticators during enrollment."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ຄວນເປັນເສັ້ນທາງໄປຍັງໄດເລກະທໍຣີພາຍໃນເທິງເຊີບເວີ, ທີ່\n"
"        privacyIDEA ມີສິດອ່ານ. ມັນຄວນຈະບັນຈຸໄຟລ໌ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ.\n"
"        ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນທຸກໃບໃນໄດເລກະທໍຣີນີ້ຈະໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມເຊື່ອຖືເພື່ອຢັ້ງຢືນ\n"
"        ອຸປະກອນຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ (authenticators) ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງໃນລະຫວ່າງການລົງທະບຽນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:334
msgid "Thumbprint of the certificate"
msgstr "ລາຍນິ້ວມື (Thumbprint) ຂອງໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ"

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:21
msgid "TiQR Authentication Server"
msgstr "ເຊີບເວີຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ TiQR"

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:66
msgid "TiQR Info URL"
msgstr "URL ຂໍ້ມູນ TiQR"

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.token.tiqr.html:54
msgid "TiQR Logo URL"
msgstr "URL ໂລໂກ້ TiQR"

