#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.push.html:1
msgid ""
"With the PUSH token privacyIDEA sends a notification to your registered smartphone asking\n"
"    if you want to approve the authentication step.\n"
"    You can accept or deny the authentication on your smartphone."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍໂທເຄັນ PUSH, privacyIDEA ຈະສົ່ງການແຈ້ງເຕືອນໄປຍັງສະມາດໂຟນທີ່ລົງທະບຽນຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"    ເພື່ອຖາມວ່າທ່ານຕ້ອງການອະນຸມັດຂັ້ນຕອນການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຫຼືບໍ່.\n"
"    ທ່ານສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນນັ້ນເທິງສະມາດໂຟນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.caconnectors.local.html:82
msgid "Working Directory"
msgstr "ໄດເລກະທໍຣີການເຮັດວຽກ"

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enroll.html:3
msgid ""
"You are about to rollover your token! This will invalidate\n"
"        your existing token\n"
"        and create a new token with a new secret key!"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານກຳລັງຈະ rollover ໂທເຄັນຂອງທ່ານ! ການເຮັດແບບນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້\n"
"        ໂທເຄັນປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານໝົດຄວາມໝາຍ\n"
"        ແລະ ສ້າງໂທເຄັນໃໝ່ພ້ອມກັບກຸນແຈລັບໃໝ່!"

#: privacyidea/static/components/login/views/login.html:12
msgid ""
"You are authenticated by the web server as user\n"
"                <b>{{ remoteUser }}</b>.\n"
"                You may log in as this user to privacyIDEA without any further\n"
"                credentials."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນໂດຍເວັບເຊີບເວີໃນນາມຜູ້ໃຊ້\n"
"                <b>{{ remoteUser }}</b>.\n"
"                ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ privacyIDEA ໃນນາມຜູ້ໃຊ້ນີ້ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້\n"
"                ຂໍ້ມູນຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນເພີ່ມຕື່ມ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/dialogs/views/dialog.lock.html:15
msgid ""
"You are logged in as {{ loggedInUser.username }}\n"
"                            @  {{ loggedInUser.realm }}."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບໃນນາມ {{ loggedInUser.username }}\n"
"                            @ {{ loggedInUser.realm }}."

#: privacyidea/static/components/directives/views/directive.containertemplate.details.html:64
msgid "You are not allowed to enroll this token type! It will be skipped!"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລົງທະບຽນໂທເຄັນປະເພດນີ້! ມັນຈະຖືກຂ້າມໄປ!"

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/controllers/containerControllers.js:918
msgid "You are not authorized to delete the following tokens:"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລຶບໂທເຄັນເຫຼົ່ານີ້:"

#: privacyidea/static/components/login/controllers/loginControllers.js:591
msgid "You are using a certain amount of Push tokens. Note, that you need a valid subscription, to use Push tokens in push mode. Otherwise Push tokens will only work in poll only mode."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານກຳລັງໃຊ້ໂທເຄັນ Push ຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງ. ໝາຍເຫດ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງມີການສະໝັກໃຊ້ທີ່ຍັງມີຜົນ, ເພື່ອໃຊ້ໂທເຄັນ Push "
"ໃນໂໝດ push. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ໂທເຄັນ Push ຈະເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ໃນໂໝດ poll ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.import.html:94
msgid ""
"You can choose a realm to which the tokens should be imported.\n"
"            You can also change the realms of each token later."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ realm ທີ່ຈະນຳເຂົ້າໂທເຄັນເຫຼົ່ານີ້.\n"
"            ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ່ຽນ realm ຂອງແຕ່ລະໂທເຄັນໄດ້ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.import.html:80
msgid "You can choose how the authenticity of the tokens to be imported should be verified."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກວິທີການກວດສອບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຂອງໂທເຄັນທີ່ຈະນຳເຂົ້າ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/config/views/config.resolvers.http.advanced.html:243
msgid ""
"You can find most of these settings in the app registration in the Entra Admin Center or you also\n"
"                    have to add them there."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດພົບການຕັ້ງຄ່າເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ໄດ້ໃນການລົງທະບຽນແອັບໃນ Entra Admin Center ຫຼື ທ່ານກໍຕ້ອງ\n"
"                    ເພີ່ມພວກມັນເຂົ້າໄປໃນນັ້ນ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/user/views/user.add.html:54
msgid ""
"You have no editable resolvers defined. So you can not write\n"
"                to any user store. If you want to add users, you need to\n"
"                <a ui-sref=\"config.resolvers.list\">define an editable\n"
"                    resolver</a>\n"
"                (like SQLResolver) and check the\n"
"                box \"Edit user store\"."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຕົວແກ້ໄຂ (resolvers) ທີ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້. ສະນັ້ນທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຂຽນ\n"
"                ຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ໃດໆ. ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມຜູ້ໃຊ້, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງ\n"
"                <a ui-sref=\"config.resolvers.list\">ກຳນົດຕົວແກ້ໄຂທີ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້</"
"a>\n"
"                (ເຊັ່ນ SQLResolver) ແລະ ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່\n"
"                ຫ້ອງ \"Edit user store\"."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enrolled.registration.html:16
msgid "You may pass this registration code to the user."
msgstr "ທ່ານອາດຈະມອບລະຫັດລົງທະບຽນນີ້ໃຫ້ກັບຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enrolled.webauthn.html:22
msgid ""
"You need to confirm the registration with your\n"
"                    authenticator. For an external authenticator, this usually\n"
"                    means pushing the button on the authenticator, or replugging\n"
"                    it (if there is no button on the authenticator). If you want\n"
"                    to use an authenticator that is integrated into your device,\n"
"                    look for a dialog box from your operating system. If you do\n"
"                    not see anything, please make sure that your authenticator\n"
"                    supports WebAuthn."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງຢືນຢັນການລົງທະບຽນກັບ\n"
"                    ອຸປະກອນຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງທ່ານ. ສຳລັບອຸປະກອນພາຍນອກ, ໂດຍປົກກະຕິແລ້ວ\n"
"                    ໝາຍເຖິງການກົດປຸ່ມເທິງອຸປະກອນ, ຫຼື ສຽບໃໝ່\n"
"                    (ຖ້າບໍ່ມີປຸ່ມເທິງອຸປະກອນ). ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການ\n"
"                    ໃຊ້ອຸປະກອນຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນທີ່ປະສົມປະສານຢູ່ໃນອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານ,\n"
"                    ໃຫ້ຊອກຫາປ່ອງຢ້ຽມໂຕ້ຕອບຈາກລະບົບປະຕິບັດການຂອງທ່ານ. ຖ້າທ່ານ\n"
"                    ບໍ່ເຫັນຫຍັງເລີຍ, ກະລຸນາໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າອຸປະກອນຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"                    ຮອງຮັບ WebAuthn."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.enrolled.u2f.html:28
msgid ""
"You need to confirm the registration with your token\n"
"                    either by pushing the blinking button or by\n"
"                    replugging your token. This depends on the actual\n"
"                    token model."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງຢືນຢັນການລົງທະບຽນກັບໂທເຄັນຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"                    ໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມທີ່ກະພິບຢູ່ ຫຼື ໂດຍການ\n"
"                    ສຽບໂທເຄັນຂອງທ່ານໃໝ່. ອັນນີ້ຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບ\n"
"                    ຮຸ່ນຂອງໂທເຄັນແທ້ໆ."

#: privacyidea/static/components/token/views/token.details.html:525
